{"tid":2320051,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有線新聞部女主播關善茹親人確診武漢肺炎 所有主播出鏡需佩戴口罩","createTime":"2020-12-10T13:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T14:33:55.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ed470a41d8e53cbc69d5a59c23527246a9112bf8","tid":2320051,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"本港新冠肺炎疫情持續，消息指，有線電視新聞部一名女主播的親友確診，女主播需要進入檢疫中心接受檢疫，有線新聞部發出指引，指示主播需要佩戴口罩上鏡報道新聞。<br />\n<br />\n有線電視回覆《香港01》查詢證實，新聞部有員工親友初步確診新冠肺炎，相關員工會安排送往檢疫。為安全起見，所有主播出鏡時都會佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，有線新聞部女主播關善茹的親人確診新冠肺炎，關被列為密切接觸者，需要送往檢疫中心接受檢疫。消息指，有線新聞部因應情況，其他主播上鏡報道新聞期間，均需要佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n有線電視回覆查詢時證實，新聞部有員工親友初步確診新冠肺炎，相關員工會安排送往檢疫。為安全起見，所有主播出鏡時都會佩戴口罩。新聞台亦已立即清潔及消毒所有新聞部的錄影廠及公眾地方，以保障同事安全。新聞部運作一切如常，不受影響，並會密切留意各同事的健康狀況。"},{"pid":"63dfbcb242101aee1fc5b0736f120a99dc3b56bb","tid":2320051,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcZvUhi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpcZvUhi.jpg&h=bb114ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edfaa5e3f9132e596f72b254e5beaa09e95cbc19","tid":2320051,"uid":76804,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"仲留低既全部都抵撚死"},{"pid":"50df0c3bb3997d5e2bba9e8bc7a3ebfd3d35860f","tid":2320051,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de3af08b4bb8b156367dda5b0cc2589390e1f10","tid":2320051,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925526a958ef4ce154096a2738f346d6a9a7782a","tid":2320051,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"有冇同四人幫除口罩傾計"},{"pid":"84c5fea3df43f1f77f9678b70c3dc6c5edf71b91","tid":2320051,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"請下假咁四位賤人咪要親身上場"},{"pid":"31e38f8bfa94e30dbbb4b604cc53d774755370d3","tid":2320051,"uid":277992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:33:15.000Z","msg":"即刻入房同四人幫傾下密偈先啦"},{"pid":"eb5f2fbb445146e49b9b1db6d0924df2ba813114","tid":2320051,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edfaa5e3f9132e596f72b254e5beaa09e95cbc19","tid":2320051,"uid":76804,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"仲留低既全部都抵撚死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"佢好似遞左信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3bf7ed26fb579fb2534af9d2cd0b4f39287d8c","tid":2320051,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"老關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}